Toys, Mobile Phones & Soybeans - With Donald Trump officially inaugurated as the 45th President, trade relations with China may be about to get serious.


A Framework for Dealing with Change - Human beings are generally metathesiophobic, i.e. we have an intrinsic fear for change.


Infusing Machines with Intelligence - Part 3 of 3 – The Ultimate Test of Human Intelligence




