Institutional Investors























 Institutional Investors

 Institutional Investors



Platinum offers its services to institutional investors through separate accounts, Platinum Trust Funds and Platinum World Portfolios plc (UCITS).

Platinum has delivered strong investment returns in global equities over 23 years in both bull and bear markets.  We believe that our contrarian long-term philosophy with a strong aversion to the conventional view means that Platinum will complement and improve most institutional fund’s existing equity portfolios.  We offer investment strategies in global equity (both long short and long only) and regional and sector specific funds including Asia, Japan and International Brands.
For further information please contact Charles Brooks, Investment Specialist on +61 2 9255 9669 or via email brooks@platinum.com.au



























