Dividend Reinvestment Plan (DRP)
23 May 2007
Platinum Asset Management Limited (ASX code PTM) has a DRP in place but it is not activated and is non-operational.
Given the limited capital requirements of a financial services organisation, such as PTM, it is currently unlikely that the Board of Directors will ever activate the DRP.






