					Full Description



		Platinum Investment Management Limited, trading as Platinum Asset Management (Platinum), operates a funds management business. The Company specializes in investing in international equities. Platinum manages approximately Australian dollar 22 billion with over 7% of this from investors in New Zealand, Europe, America and Asia. It offers regional and industry-specific funds in addition to global portfolios. It provides investment management services to its related party unit trusts - the Platinum Trust Funds and Platinum Global Fund; its offshore fund, Platinum World Portfolios Plc., and its two Australian Securities Exchange Limited (ASX)-listed investment companies (LICs), Platinum Capital Limited and Platinum Asia Investments Limited. Platinum's product range consists of global, regional and sector products for investment. Its Platinum Trust Funds include Platinum International Fund, Platinum Unhedged Fund, Platinum Asia Fund, Platinum Japan Fund and Platinum European Fund.
